title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-9.8 - Distribution of human milk
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-9.8 - Distribution of human milk

State Regulations

Facilities shall distribute human milk only upon receipt of a written order from a licensed physician. Notes

comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
